- cs.PF (Performance) is also likely as the paper focuses on performance monitoring and optimization. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the LIKWID monitoring stack is a software framework. 
- cs.AR (Architecture) is another possible category as the paper discusses hardware performance monitoring. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses system monitoring and integration with existing monitoring infrastructures.
